  Release notes
  =============
  
  TransMac can open Macintosh format disk drives, flash drives, 
  CD-ROMs, DVDs, high density diskettes, dmg and sparseimage files.

  Features:
  
  *  Read and write Mac format disks, CDs, DVDs, high density floppies 
     and disk images (dmg and sparseimage).
  *  Supports standard HFS (Mac OS Standard), HFS+ (Mac OS Extended) 
     and HFSX (with case sensitive file names) volumes.
  *  Access Mac volumes on boot drive (like Boot Camp).
  *  Create, read, write and compress Mac disk images (dmg and sparseimage).
  *  Built in burner software to create Mac format CDs and DVDs (including 
     dual-layer).
  *  Burn ISO and dmg files to CD/DVD.
  *  Format disks for use on Mac.
  *  Read Mac multisession and hybrid CDs.
  
  TransMac supports Windows 2000, XP, Vista, Server 2003/2008.
  
  
  Install notes
  =============
  
  1. Install TransMac 8.1
  2. Replace TransMac.exe with the provided one
  3. Run the program, register with any name and serial
